{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"94e3549889","title":"罗瑞卿在华北五省及山东省暨省属各市公安会议上的开幕词（节录）","origin":"《取缔反动会道门工作历史资料汇编（1948－1992年）》，公安部一局编印， 2009年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"616d31ffcd","index":0,"year":1949,"month":12,"day":13,"articleId":"94e3549889"}],"tags":[{"id":"6c3c62f283","name":"罗瑞卿","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2f168430f5","type":"title","text":"罗瑞卿在华北五省及山东省暨省属各市公安会议上的开幕词（节录）（记录稿）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"910cdf4f13","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"7e1b279533","type":"paragraph","text":"此外，农村中、城市中的封建残余势力，社会上的游离分子，如：流氓、会门、盗匪等等，甚至群众中的一时的不觉悟的现象，以及一些资产阶级的小资产阶级的情绪，以致于我们的每一件困难，在在都可以被敌人抓去利用的。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"3b726e4e7b","type":"subtitle","text":"……","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"5ff75d448d","type":"paragraph","text":"至于会道门问题，则大体须在群众有了初步或充分发动以后。这是一般的规律，不是绝对机械的，同时亦必须看出所有步骤之间的联系性。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"ad3970988f","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"f223047685","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的面前是确实还存在着敌人的。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"4fb89cf55d","type":"paragraph","text":"是一些什么力量会破坏我们的生产建设呢？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"6e321df9c2","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，是特务分子及残余的国民党的潜伏反动力量；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"982d5efb7c","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，是残余的小股土匪，特别是带有政治性的土匪；","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"53a5b41b4a","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，残余的封建势力，其中包括不安分的企图复辟的地富分子、会门帮会等黑暗势力；","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"7aabecf484","type":"paragraph","text":"第四，返乡人员中隐藏着的反动分子；","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"690b8b243a","type":"paragraph","text":"第五，社会的游离分子，即不事生产的流氓，其中也包括少数从革命队伍中分化出去的蜕化分子。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"},{"id":"23601141b2","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889"}],"page":{"id":"3c62e8ad77","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"94e3549889","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}